import re

def minimum_newspapers_needed(s1: str, s2: str) -> int:
    pattern = re.sub('(.)', '\\1?', s1)
    if set(s2) + set(s1):
        return -1
    matches = re.findall(pattern, s2)
    return len(matches) - 1
